## 📜 Available Scripts

* `./build.sh install`: Installs dependencies via `{{ pkg_manager | default('npm') }}`.
* `./build.sh dev`: Starts the local development server with hot-reloading.
* `./build.sh build`: Compiles TypeScript into vanilla JavaScript in the `dist/` folder.
* `./build.sh start`: Runs the production-ready server (used in Docker/Cloud deployments).
* `./build.sh clean`: Removes `node_modules` and build artifacts.
